OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FElaine Willcox has been speaking to
OL,8,FBells, a mum who is fighting a change
OL,9,Fin the welfare system after being
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with terminal cancer.
OL,12,FA mum with terminal bowel cancer who
OL,13,F"wasted months of precious time" with
OL,14,Fher family applying for benefits is
OL,15,Fcalling for the system to be
OL,16,Fsimplified.
