OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FBells, 56, spent 14 months going
OL,7,Fthrough appeals for Personal
OL,8,FIndependent Payments (PIP) as she was
OL,9,Funable to work during her cancer
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,FThe mum-of-two claims during her 90-
OL,13,Fminute interview a Department for Work
OL,14,Fand Pensions (DWP) medical assessor
OL,15,F"did not know where her bowel was"
OL,16,Fbefore rejecting her application.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
