OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FShe said: "I expected help because I
OL,7,Fhave paid into the system all of my
OL,8,Flife. I've never lied. I've never
OL,9,Fcheated. I've never done anything
OL,10,Fwrong.
OL,12,F"She asked me what my illness was and
OL,13,FI said bowel cancer. She said 'which
OL,14,Fpart of the body is that?' and I
OL,15,Fthought 'oh God.' They asked how far I
OL,16,Fcan walk in the length of a double
OL,17,Fdecker bus - it was ridiculous."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
