OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FBells said with an uncertain future
OL,7,Fshe wanted to spend precious time with
OL,8,Ffamily and friends, but was forced to
OL,9,Fwaste months trying to navigate the
OL,10,Fcomplicated benefit paperwork
OL,12,F"It took me three gos to go through
OL,13,Fthe door. I chatted to the benefits
OL,14,Fgirls at Maggie's and you get a huge
OL,15,Fform in the post", she said.
OL,17,FWith the help of cancer charity
OL,18,FMaggie's and her local MP, Aphra
OL,19,FBrandreth, Bells, from Chester, is
OL,20,Fcalling for a special cancer benefit
OL,21,Fto simplify the process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
