OL,3,CMum with terminal cancer 'wastes' 14
OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,FShe added: "The irony is if they gave
OL,7,Fus the support quicker - we would be
OL,8,Fback in the economy quicker. We would
OL,9,Fbe off their books faster."
OL,11,FA Department for Work and Pensions
OL,12,Fsaid: "We support millions of people
OL,13,Fthrough our welfare system every year
OL,14,Fand it is a priority people receive
OL,15,Fthe benefits they are entitled to as
OL,16,Fquickly as possible.
