OL,4,Cmonths applying for benefits
OL,6,F"We have hired more staff to respond
OL,7,Fto an increased volume of claims and
OL,8,Fhave special rules in place so that
OL,9,Fpeople nearing the end of their life
OL,10,Fare guaranteed a fast-tracked PIP
OL,11,Faward.
OL,13,F"On the rare occasion this does not
OL,14,Fhappen, we will investigate to
OL,15,Funderstand what went wrong."
